---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import LocalSEO from '../components/LocalSEO.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Protection Review | Free Insurance Audit | PCFG Insurance" description="Schedule your free Complete Protection Review. 61% of families have dangerous coverage gaps. Our comprehensive audit finds gaps, eliminates waste, and ensures you're fully protected." ogImage="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3760067/pexels-photo-3760067.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200&h=630" ogType="website">
  <LocalSEO pageName="Complete Protection Review" pageDescription="Free comprehensive insurance audit to find coverage gaps and ensure complete protection" />
  <Header />
  
  <main id="main-content">
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white" role="banner">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-6 font-heading">
            Is Your Insurance Actually Protecting You?
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-primary font-semibold mb-4">
            61% of families have dangerous coverage gaps they don't know about
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-neutral-dark max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
            Schedule your free Complete Protection Review — a comprehensive audit of your insurance coverage to find gaps, eliminate waste, and ensure you're fully protected.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="https://calendly.com/pcfginsurance/complete-protection-review" class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200 shadow-lg">
              Schedule My Free Review
            </a>
            <a href="tel:877-717-7234" class="border-2 border-primary text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition-colors duration-200">
              Call (877) 717-7234
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Problem Section: Swiss Cheese Insurance -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white" aria-labelledby="problem-heading">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 id="problem-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-6 font-heading">
            Most People Have "Swiss Cheese" Insurance
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-neutral-dark max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            You have insurance. But do you have the RIGHT insurance?
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Gap 1 -->
          <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-500">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-red-700 mb-2">Jewelry, Art, Collectibles</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">Limited to $1,500–$2,500 on most homeowners policies. That $20,000 ring? Not fully covered.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Gap 2 -->
          <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-500">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-red-700 mb-2">Home-Based Businesses</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">Not covered by homeowners insurance at all. Your Etsy shop or consulting business is exposed.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Gap 3 -->
          <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-500">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-red-700 mb-2">Side Hustles & Gig Work</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">Personal auto and home policies exclude commercial use. Uber, DoorDash, freelance work — not protected.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Gap 4 -->
          <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-500">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-red-700 mb-2">Inadequate Liability Limits</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">$300K–$500K isn't enough in today's lawsuit environment. One accident could wipe out everything.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Gap 5 -->
          <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-500">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-red-700 mb-2">Missing Umbrella Coverage</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">Most families need it. Most don't have it. $1M+ protection costs less than Netflix.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Gap 6 -->
          <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-500">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-red-700 mb-2">Flood & Earthquake Exclusions</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">Standard policies exclude these perils. Are you in a flood zone? You might not know until it's too late.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-red-600">
            The scary part: You don't know what you don't know. Until something happens.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Solution Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white" aria-labelledby="solution-heading">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 id="solution-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-6 font-heading">
            The Complete Protection Review
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-neutral-dark max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            A 30-minute comprehensive audit of your insurance coverage
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Personal Coverage -->
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Personal Coverage</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-dark">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Homeowners/renters — replacement cost adequacy</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Auto insurance — liability limits and gap coverage</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Umbrella insurance — do you need it? (Probably yes)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Valuables — jewelry, art, collectibles scheduling</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Flood & earthquake — exposure assessment</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Business & Side Income -->
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Business & Side Income</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-dark">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Home-based business coverage</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Side hustle protection (Etsy, consulting, etc.)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Gig economy coverage (Uber, DoorDash)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Short-term rental exposure (Airbnb, VRBO)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Professional liability needs</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Family Protection -->
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Family Protection</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-dark">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Life insurance adequacy</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Disability insurance</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Health insurance optimization</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
                <span>Long-term care planning</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- What You Get -->
        <div class="mt-16 bg-primary-dark text-white p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">What You Get</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
            <div>
              <div class="text-4xl mb-2">📋</div>
              <p class="font-semibold">Detailed Gap Analysis Report</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-4xl mb-2">📋</div>
              <p class="font-semibold">Prioritized Recommendations</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-4xl mb-2">💰</div>
              <p class="font-semibold">Quotes for Needed Coverage</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-4xl mb-2">✋</div>
              <p class="font-semibold">No Obligation — Ever</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Social Proof Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white" aria-labelledby="testimonials-heading">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 id="testimonials-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-6 font-heading">
            What Clients Say About Their Protection Review
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
            <div class="text-4xl text-primary mb-4">"</div>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark mb-6 italic">
              I had no idea my $20,000 engagement ring was only covered for $1,500. Marcus helped me schedule it properly. Two months later, it was stolen. Full replacement value paid. Worth every penny of the premium.
            </p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-primary">— Sarah K.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
            <div class="text-4xl text-primary mb-4">"</div>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark mb-6 italic">
              I drive for Uber on weekends. My 'personal' auto policy would have denied any claim while I was working. The rideshare endorsement cost $150/year. That's nothing compared to the peace of mind.
            </p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-primary">— Mike T.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
            <div class="text-4xl text-primary mb-4">"</div>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark mb-6 italic">
              The review found I was underinsured by $400K on my home replacement cost. Construction costs have skyrocketed. My old policy wouldn't have rebuilt my house. Fixed that before renewal.
            </p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-primary">— Jennifer L.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Process Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white" aria-labelledby="process-heading">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 id="process-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-6 font-heading">
            How It Works
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <!-- Step 1 -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">1</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">Schedule</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">Pick a 30-minute time slot that works for you — phone or Zoom.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Step 2 -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">2</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">The Review</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">We'll go through your current policies, discuss your assets and risks, and identify gaps.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">3</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">Your Report</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">You'll receive a written summary of findings and prioritized recommendations.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Step 4 -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">4</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">Decision</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">Implement recommendations now, later, or never. No pressure.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 id="faq-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-6 font-heading">
            Frequently Asked Questions
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- FAQ 1 -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">Is this really free?</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">Yes. The Complete Protection Review is complimentary for existing and prospective clients.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- FAQ 2 -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">Will you try to sell me a bunch of insurance?</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">I'll show you gaps and provide quotes. You decide what to do. Many clients implement everything. Some implement nothing. Both are fine.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- FAQ 3 -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">I already reviewed my insurance recently. Do I need this?</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">If it was just a "renewal review" checking boxes, probably yes. Most agents don't dig into valuables, side hustles, liability adequacy, or umbrella needs.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- FAQ 4 -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">How often should I do this?</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">Annually, or whenever you have a major life change (new home, baby, marriage, inheritance, new business).</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- FAQ 5 -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">What if I have insurance with multiple companies?</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-dark">Even better reason to do this. Fragmented coverage often creates gaps. We'll look at the big picture.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Final CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-primary-dark text-white" role="complementary">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading">
          Don't Wait for a Claim to Find Out You're Not Covered
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8">
          Insurance is like a parachute. If it doesn't work when you need it, you'll never need it again.
        </p>
        
        <div class="mb-8">
          <a href="https://calendly.com/pcfginsurance/complete-protection-review" class="inline-block bg-white text-primary-dark hover:bg-gray-100 px-10 py-5 rounded-lg font-bold text-xl transition-colors duration-200 shadow-lg">
            Schedule My Free Complete Protection Review
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          Or call us directly: <a href="tel:877-717-7234" class="underline hover:text-gray-200">(877) 717-7234</a>
        </p>
        
        <div class="mt-8 text-left max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-primary-700 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4">What happens next:</h3>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Pick a time that works for you</li>
            <li>We'll send a brief pre-review checklist</li>
            <li>Show up (phone or Zoom) for 30 minutes</li>
            <li>Get your report within 24 hours</li>
            <li>Sleep better knowing you're protected</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>